OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782776882
OL,3,CMet Police apologise for failures in
OL,4,Chandling 19-year-old gay student's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FWords by Georgia Ziebart, Senior
OL,8,FInvestigations Producer
OL,10,FThe Metropolitan Police has apologised
OL,11,Fto the family of 19-year-old Ed Cornes
OL,12,Ffollowing an ITV News investigation
OL,13,Finto the handling of his death.
OL,15,FThe force said on Monday that
OL,16,Fspecialist officers were reviewing the
OL,17,Foriginal investigation, and are
OL,18,Fappealing for further information from
OL,19,Fwitnesses.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
