PN,31602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782776882
OL,3,CMet Police apologise for failures in
OL,4,Chandling 19-year-old gay student's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FEd, who was gay, was just two days
OL,8,Finto his first term at University
OL,9,FCollege London when he died in 2021.
OL,10,FTwo men were arrested on suspicion of
OL,11,Fmurder, but were later released
OL,12,Fwithout charges.
OL,14,FHis family has previously told ITV
OL,15,FNews that police failures, driven by
OL,16,Fhomophobia, meant the circumstances of
OL,17,Fhis death were never properly
OL,18,Finvestigated.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782776882
OL,3,CMet Police apologise for failures in
OL,4,Chandling 19-year-old gay student's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FEd's mother, Miriam Blythe, told ITV
OL,8,FNews on Monday that the apology feels
OL,9,F"shallow" and "too little too late".
OL,11,F"It's a small victory. I am pleased
OL,12,Fthey are doing a review, and I hope
OL,13,Fjustice will be served in the end.
OL,15,F"But it's been a horrible, devastating
OL,16,Fstruggle where I always knew I was
OL,17,Fright, and had multiple police
OL,18,Fofficers telling me I was wrong.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782776882
OL,3,CMet Police apologise for failures in
OL,4,Chandling 19-year-old gay student's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,F"Your son dies in horrible
OL,8,Fcircumstances and then the police say
OL,9,Fit's all his fault. It's been
OL,10,Fdevastating."
OL,12,FEd's body was found in a basement room
OL,13,Fof a hotel in King's Cross, central
OL,14,FLondon, around five minutes from his
OL,15,Fhalls of residence. Other students
OL,16,Fsaid he was "very drunk" that evening.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
