PN,31605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782776882
OL,3,CMet Police apologise for failures in
OL,4,Chandling 19-year-old gay student's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FAccording to the inquest into his
OL,8,Fdeath, in the early hours of the
OL,9,Fmorning, he left his halls and met
OL,10,FMatthew Butler, 55, a man he had never
OL,11,Fmet before, who took him to the hotel.
OL,12,FInside the room was another man, Ian
OL,13,FCasimir, 58.
OL,15,FEd was found dead several hours later.
OL,17,FHis inquest heard he was found with 36
OL,18,Fcuts and other injuries, and with high
OL,19,Flevels of the drug GHB in his
OL,20,Fbloodstream.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782776882
OL,3,CMet Police apologise for failures in
OL,4,Chandling 19-year-old gay student's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FThe two older men he was with had
OL,8,Fdelayed calling an ambulance while
OL,9,Fthey attempted to put Ed's clothes
OL,10,Fback on and repositioned his body.
OL,12,FButler and Casimir were arrested on
OL,13,Fsuspicion of murder and then later
OL,14,Freleased without charge. ITV News has
OL,15,Fpreviously tried unsuccessfully to
OL,16,Freach both men for comment.
OL,18,FMiriam Blythe told ITV News in
OL,19,FFebruary that the Metropolitan Police
OL,20,Fhad treated the family "appallingly"
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782776882
OL,3,CMet Police apologise for failures in
OL,4,Chandling 19-year-old gay student's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FEd's mother, Miriam, accused the
OL,8,Fpolice investigation of being deeply
OL,9,Fflawed from the outset.
OL,11,FShe told ITV News' Sejal Karia that
OL,12,Fkey witnesses were never spoken to,
OL,13,Fand that vital evidence was lost `
OL,14,Fincluding CCTV and blood samples.
OL,16,FMiriam lodged multiple complaints with
OL,17,Fthe Metropolitan Police and with its
OL,18,Fwatchdog. An internal review later
OL,19,Ffound 27 failings.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782776882
OL,3,CMet Police apologise for failures in
OL,4,Chandling 19-year-old gay student's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FShe previously told ITV News that the
OL,8,Fpolice's failure to investigate Ed's
OL,9,Fdeath properly was rooted in
OL,10,Fhomophobia and assumptions they had
OL,11,Fmade about his lifestyle.
OL,13,FShe said officers had made overtly
OL,14,Fhomophobic comments to her, including
OL,15,Fthat "with man-on-man sex, anything
OL,16,Fcan happen".
OL,18,FThe Met has since acknowledged that an
OL,19,Fofficer made those comments and has
OL,20,Fapologised for the upset caused to the
OL,21,Ffamily.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782776882
OL,3,CMet Police apologise for failures in
OL,4,Chandling 19-year-old gay student's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FBut they also previously claimed that
OL,8,FEd's death had been properly
OL,9,Finvestigated and that all lines of
OL,10,Fenquiry had been fully explored.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
