PN,31610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782776882
OL,3,CMet Police apologise for failures in
OL,4,Chandling 19-year-old gay student's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FIn a statement on Monday, the
OL,8,FMetropolitan Police said: "We
OL,9,Fapologise for the pain caused to
OL,10,FEdward's family through the handling
OL,11,Fof our investigation. We acknowledge
OL,12,Fthat aspects of the initial
OL,13,Finvestigation were not handled
OL,14,Fcorrectly and did not meet the high
OL,15,Fstandards we expect.
OL,17,F"We have since met with Edward's
OL,18,Ffamily to apologise in person and
OL,19,Frecognise the distress our actions
OL,20,Fhave caused.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782776882
OL,3,CMet Police apologise for failures in
OL,4,Chandling 19-year-old gay student's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,F"Specialist officers are now reviewing
OL,8,Fthe original investigation into
OL,9,FEdward's death and surrounding
OL,10,Fcircumstances to determine if there
OL,11,Fare any possible further lines of
OL,12,Fenquiry.
OL,14,F"We remain in contact with the family
OL,15,Fand will continue to keep them updated
OL,16,Fas our work progresses."
OL,18,FAn independent investigation by the
OL,19,FIOPC remains ongoing. A spokesperson
OL,20,Ffor the IOPC said:
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
