PN,31612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782776882
OL,3,CMet Police apologise for failures in
OL,4,Chandling 19-year-old gay student's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,F"We are independently investigating a
OL,8,Fnumber of complaints about the Met
OL,9,FPolice regarding its handling of the
OL,10,Ftragic death of 19 year old Edward
OL,11,FCornes, who was found dead in a London
OL,12,Fhotel in October 2021.
OL,14,F"Those complaints include alleged
OL,15,Ffailures in the investigation into
OL,16,FEdward's death, its handling of the
OL,17,Fsubsequent coronial proceedings and
OL,18,Finquest, including evidence provided
OL,19,Fby an officer at the inquest and its
OL,20,Fcommunication with Edward's family
OL,21,Fthroughout.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782776882
OL,3,CMet Police apologise for failures in
OL,4,Chandling 19-year-old gay student's
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,F"His family made several complaints to
OL,8,Fthe Met which voluntarily referred the
OL,9,Fmatters to the IOPC on 6 February and
OL,10,Ffurther matters on 17 February.
OL,12,F"We have been liaising with Edward's
OL,13,Ffamily to determine the scope and
OL,14,Fbreadth of our investigation and we
OL,15,Fwill keep them regularly updated as
OL,16,Four enquiries progress."
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
